### **🚀 Step 1: AI Memory Core Setup**
I’m generating the **base structure** for the AI Memory Core, which will store everything AI-merged Jesse needs to operate **without losing context.**  

This will include:
✔️ **Your Background & Skills** – All professional experience, key achievements.  
✔️ **Decisions & Strategy** – Past choices, why they were made, what worked.  
✔️ **Goals & Constraints** – Where we’re headed, what must be optimized.  

⏳ **Generating now...** One moment.
